Diageo’s Kenyan Unit Appoints Bonney as Executive, Business Daily Reports

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-07-28T04:30:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/diageo-s-kenyan-unit-appoints-bonney-as-executive-business-daily-reports.html
Diageo Plc (DGE) ’s Kenyan unit named Jojo
Bonney as head of EABL International to strengthen its sales
team, Business Daily reported, citing a note to staff by Chief
Executive Officer Seni Adetu.  Bonney was previously the sales director at Ghana Breweries
Ltd., the Nairobi-based newspaper said. He replaces Patricia
Ithau, who quit the company in March, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Paul Richardson  at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  